{"tid":238941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（理性討論）皇馬有今時今日嘅絕對實至名歸","createTime":"2017-05-11T10:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T10:51:02.000Z","uid":65386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed04bb1bf8f124f0726019e9e4cdb249823394f","tid":238941,"uid":65386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:39:56.000Z","msg":"你話皇馬金錢足球 買曬啲球星翻黎邊夠你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地又交到成績喎 雙線叫糊 睇下獌狗嗰邊又伊巴普巴mk仲做緊6弟 爭隻霸氣杯淪落到讓賽俾阿記咁滯<br />\n<br />\n你話佢地班球員唔圑結 但佢地到關鍵時刻爭勝心就好強 今季好多時候都玩到反cup 呢樣其他隊真係無乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最重要一點 當巴塞全盛時期嗰陣以為可以稱霸地球 開始唔玩青訓同放走曬啲板凳球員 小白影帝呢班老囇咪收曬皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n相反皇馬 積極提升青訓同搵定啲接班人 今時今日先可以玩到二隊都咁屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49604eaa2a9ff82921be08960ccb25831996a58c","tid":238941,"uid":35501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"咁早燈定<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a207322ec0f14ef8417eaffa96a9552d3d05cfc1","tid":238941,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:51:02.000Z","msg":"皇馬青訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}